            <div class="title">
                United States Air Force (United Kingdom Bases)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1954-01-09/debates/b52a0076-884f-4b6e-bb4c-341e55b2943c/PolicyDocuments(MinisterialResponsibility)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
