            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-052dbe00-ba12-4493-b168-9e4323edb52c">
                Mr. Emrys Hughes
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-052dbe00-ba12-4493-b168-9e4323edb52c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-01-09/debates/63ff1c4b-fa51-46eb-b5d7-e7ce9a8eaa58/UnitedStatesAirForce(UnitedKingdomBases)#contribution-052dbe00-ba12-4493-b168-9e4323edb52c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does the Prime Minister still adhere to the point of view that this country is in greater danger as the result of the American Air Force being here?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-052dbe00-ba12-4493-b168-9e4323edb52c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-01-09/debates/63ff1c4b-fa51-46eb-b5d7-e7ce9a8eaa58/UnitedStatesAirForce(UnitedKingdomBases)#contribution-052dbe00-ba12-4493-b168-9e4323edb52c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-01-09/debates/63ff1c4b-fa51-46eb-b5d7-e7ce9a8eaa58/UnitedStatesAirForce(UnitedKingdomBases)#contribution-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think that I have stated that point of view in the sense that we were in the front line, and that is quite true. But the general policy of the late Government in rearming in conjunction with the United States and in making strong defence arrangements has played a noticeable and traceable part in the relaxation and diminution of tension which has occurred. I think that they deserve full credit for their action, in which we supported them, and which is being continued subject to the general tendency of events.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-01-09/debates/63ff1c4b-fa51-46eb-b5d7-e7ce9a8eaa58/UnitedStatesAirForce(UnitedKingdomBases)#contribution-dd31d12e-5873-4836-a08b-20f8e1457e25">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
